verses.verse: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise,<s%> O you <S%H5650>servants<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> <S%H1984>praise<s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD.<s%>
<S%H1288>Blessed<s%> be the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> from this time forth and for ever <S%H5769>more.<s%>
From the <S%H4217>rising<s%> of the <S%H8121>sun<s%> to the <S%H3996>going<s%> down of the same the <S%H3068>LORD's<s%> <S%H8034>name<s%> is to be <S%H1984>praised.<s%>
<S%H4310>Who<s%> is like to the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> our <S%H430>God,<s%> who <S%H3427>dwells<s%> on <S%H1361>high,<s%>
Who <S%H8213>humbles<s%> himself to <S%H7200>behold<s%> the things that are in <S%H8064>heaven,<s%> and in the <S%H776>earth!<s%>
He <S%H6965>raises<s%> up the <S%H1800>poor<s%> out of the <S%H6083>dust,<s%> and <S%H7311>lifts<s%> the <S%H34>needy<s%> out of the <S%H830>dunghill;<s%>
That he may <S%H3427>set<s%> him with <S%H5081>princes,<s%> even with the <S%H5081>princes<s%> of his <S%H5971>people.<s%>
He makes the <S%H6135>barren<s%> woman to keep <S%H1004>house,<s%> and to be a <S%H8056>joyful<s%> <S%H517>mother<s%> of <S%H1121>children.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%>
